data.description: Step into a world of serene living with this cozy 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence nestled just moments from RT 62. The home's allure lies in its open kitchen design that frames breathtaking Joshua Tree vistas, complemented by a sleek, upgraded bathroom boasting a modern walk-in shower. Set on a large fenced lot, this property invites your imagination to shape the outdoor space into your dream retreat. A detached 2-car garage stands ready for secure parking or as a versatile workspace, while starlit nights in the backyard offer an enchanting tranquility. Embrace the vibrant community spirit with antique shops, charming wine bodega, cozy coffee houses, and delightful eateries all within easy reach.; just minutes from Joshua Tree National Park and Pioneer Town. Adding to its allure, a room with a private entrance presents versatile possibilities--a secluded haven, a productive home office, or an inviting guest suite. This home invites you to explore its endless potential, offering an unparalleled opportunity to curate your ideal living space amidst the charm of Old Town Yucca Valley.
